## Hints for Future Agents
- Literal handling mirrors SQL rendering: bool literals become 1/0,
  dict/list literals compare as minified JSON text.
- $eq with literal None is IS NULL; NOT(NULL) is NULL (filtered out) — SQL
  three-valued logic, not Python truthiness.
- turn_ids in CallsFilter is intentionally ignored (sqlite parity).
- LIMIT quirks ported exactly: limit 0 or negative = unlimited; offset <= 0
  ignored.
- summary.weave.trace_name is sortable but NOT queryable (sqlite parity —
  the query-side transform lacks the trace_name CASE).

